/-- **`ūĚĒě(ő∑)/ūĚĒě(ő∑‚āÄ)` principal as a fractional ideal `‚üĻ` `IsPrincipal(ūĚĒě(ő∑)/ūĚĒě‚āÄ)`.**

The anchored quotient `ūĚĒě(ő∑)/ūĚĒě‚āÄ` (`ūĚĒě‚āÄ = aEtaZeroDvdPPow`, the `ūĚĒ≠`-coprime part of `ūĚĒě(ő∑‚āÄ)`) is
principal whenever the *root* quotient `ūĚĒě(ő∑)/ūĚĒě(ő∑‚āÄ)` is principal as a fractional ideal.  The `ūĚĒ≠^m`
correction is principal (`ūĚĒ≠ = (ő∂-1)` is principal), so it cannot break principality.  Mirrors the
final ideal-bookkeeping steps of `caseII_a_div_a_zero_isPrincipal_of_realIdealModel`
(`SpecificDischarge.lean`), but driven by the bare fractional-ideal principality of `ūĚĒě(ő∑)/ūĚĒě(ő∑‚āÄ)`
rather than by a `ūĚďě K‚Āļ` real-ideal-model witness. -/
theorem caseII_isPrincipal_aDivAEtaZero_of_rootQuotientPrincipal
    {K : Type} [Field K] [NumberField K] [IsCyclotomicExtension {37} ‚Ąö K]
    [NumberField.IsCMField K] (hp : (37 : ‚Ąē) ‚Č† 2)
    {ő∂ : K} (hő∂ : IsPrimitiveRoot ő∂ 37)
    {x y z : ūĚďě K} {őĶ : (ūĚďě K)ň£} {m : ‚Ąē}
    (e : x ^ 37 + y ^ 37 = őĶ * ((hő∂.toInteger - 1) ^ (m + 1) * z) ^ 37)
    (hy : ¬¨ hő∂.toInteger - 1 ‚ą£ y)
    (ő∑ : nthRootsFinset 37 (1 : ūĚďě K))
    (h_root :
      Submodule.IsPrincipal
        (((rootDivZetaSubOneDvdGcd hp hő∂ e hy ő∑) /
          (rootDivZetaSubOneDvdGcd hp hő∂ e hy
            (zetaSubOneDvdRoot hp hő∂ e hy))
          : FractionalIdeal (ūĚďě K)‚Āį K) : Submodule (ūĚďě K) K)) :
    Submodule.IsPrincipal
      ((rootDivZetaSubOneDvdGcd hp hő∂ e hy ő∑ /
        aEtaZeroDvdPPow hp hő∂ e hy
        : FractionalIdeal (ūĚďě K)‚Āį K) : Submodule (ūĚďě K) K) := by
  haveI : Fact (Nat.Prime 37) := ‚ü®by decide‚ü©
  rw [‚Üź a_eta_zero_dvd_p_pow_spec, mul_comm, FractionalIdeal.coeIdeal_mul,
      ‚Üź div_div, FractionalIdeal.isPrincipal_iff] at h_root
  obtain ‚ü®a, ha‚ü© := h_root
  rw [div_eq_iff, Ideal.span_singleton_pow, FractionalIdeal.coeIdeal_span_singleton,
    FractionalIdeal.spanSingleton_mul_spanSingleton] at ha
  ¬∑ rw [FractionalIdeal.isPrincipal_iff]
    exact ‚ü®_, ha‚ü©
  ¬∑ rw [‚Üź FractionalIdeal.coeIdeal_bot,
      (FractionalIdeal.coeIdeal_injective' (le_rfl : (ūĚďě K)‚Āį ‚Č§ (ūĚďě K)‚Āį)).ne_iff]
    apply mt eq_zero_of_pow_eq_zero
    rw [Ideal.zero_eq_bot, Ideal.span_singleton_eq_bot]
    exact hő∂.toInteger_isPrimitiveRoot.sub_one_ne_zero (by decide : (1 : ‚Ąē) < 37)


/-- **`[ūĚĒě(ő∑)] = [ūĚĒě(ő∑‚āÄ)]` (class equality) `‚üĻ` `ūĚĒě(ő∑)/ūĚĒě(ő∑‚āÄ)` principal as a fractional ideal.**

Stated on a `CaseIIData37` datum `D` (so the root-ideal nonvanishing comes from
`caseII_rootIdeal_ne_bot D`).
The pure class-group statement `[ūĚĒě(ő∑)] = [ūĚĒě(ő∑‚āÄ)]` in `Cl(ūĚďě K)` is, by `ClassGroup.mk0_eq_mk0_iff`,
the existence of `a, b ‚Č† 0` with `(a)¬∑ūĚĒě(ő∑) = (b)¬∑ūĚĒě(ő∑‚āÄ)`, which exhibits `ūĚĒě(ő∑)/ūĚĒě(ő∑‚āÄ) = (b/a)` as a
principal fractional ideal. -/
theorem caseII_rootQuotientPrincipal_of_classEq
    {K : Type} [Field K] [NumberField K] [IsCyclotomicExtension {37} ‚Ąö K]
    [NumberField.IsCMField K] {m : ‚Ąē} (D : CaseIIData37 K m) (hp : (37 : ‚Ąē) ‚Č† 2)
    (ő∑ : nthRootsFinset 37 (1 : ūĚďě K))
    (h_classEq :
      ClassGroup.mk0 ‚ü®D.rootIdeal ő∑,
          mem_nonZeroDivisors_iff_ne_zero.mpr
            (by rw [Ideal.zero_eq_bot]; exact caseII_rootIdeal_ne_bot D hp ő∑)‚ü© =
        ClassGroup.mk0 ‚ü®D.rootIdeal D.etaZero,
          mem_nonZeroDivisors_iff_ne_zero.mpr
            (by rw [Ideal.zero_eq_bot]; exact caseII_rootIdeal_ne_bot D hp D.etaZero)‚ü©) :
    Submodule.IsPrincipal
      (((D.rootIdeal ő∑) / (D.rootIdeal D.etaZero)
        : FractionalIdeal (ūĚďě K)‚Āį K) : Submodule (ūĚďě K) K) := by
  haveI : Fact (Nat.Prime 37) := ‚ü®by decide‚ü©
  obtain ‚ü®a, b, ha, hb, hab‚ü© := ClassGroup.mk0_eq_mk0_iff.mp h_classEq
  -- a ‚Č† 0 as a fractional-ideal spanSingleton scalar.
  have haK : (a : K) ‚Č† 0 := by
    simpa using (FaithfulSMul.algebraMap_injective (ūĚďě K) K).ne ha
  have hsa_ne : FractionalIdeal.spanSingleton (ūĚďě K)‚Āį (a : K) ‚Č† 0 :=
    FractionalIdeal.spanSingleton_ne_zero_iff.mpr haK
  -- Coerce (a)¬∑ūĚĒě(ő∑) = (b)¬∑ūĚĒě(ő∑‚āÄ) to fractional ideals.
  have hcoe := congrArg
    (fun (I : Ideal (ūĚďě K)) ‚Ü¶ (I : FractionalIdeal (ūĚďě K)‚Āį K)) hab
  simp only [FractionalIdeal.coeIdeal_mul, FractionalIdeal.coeIdeal_span_singleton] at hcoe
  -- ūĚĒě(ő∑) = spanSingleton(b/a) ¬∑ ūĚĒě(ő∑‚āÄ): cancel spanSingleton(a) from `hcoe`.
  have hkey : (D.rootIdeal ő∑ : FractionalIdeal (ūĚďě K)‚Āį K) =
      FractionalIdeal.spanSingleton (ūĚďě K)‚Āį ((b : K) / (a : K)) *
        (D.rootIdeal D.etaZero : FractionalIdeal (ūĚďě K)‚Āį K) := by
    apply mul_left_cancel‚āÄ hsa_ne
    rw [hcoe, ‚Üź mul_assoc, FractionalIdeal.spanSingleton_mul_spanSingleton,
      mul_div_cancel‚āÄ _ haK]
  rw [FractionalIdeal.isPrincipal_iff]
  refine ‚ü®(b : K) / (a : K), ?_‚ü©
  rw [hkey, mul_div_assoc, div_self
    (by
      rw [‚Üź FractionalIdeal.coeIdeal_bot,
        (FractionalIdeal.coeIdeal_injective' (le_rfl : (ūĚďě K)‚Āį ‚Č§ (ūĚďě K)‚Āį)).ne_iff]
      exact caseII_rootIdeal_ne_bot D hp D.etaZero),
    mul_one]

