i.e. `c ‚ąą Cl‚ĀĽ[37]`) under the proven Vandiver `37 ‚ą§ h‚Āļ` ‚ÄĒ but `Cl‚ĀĽ(ūĚďě K)[37]` is **nonzero**, so
