/-- **The single-root principalization predicate from the sharp class-equality residual.**

From `CaseIIAdjacentAnchoredClassTrivial37` (the pure `[ūĚĒě(ő∑)] = [ūĚĒě(ő∑‚āÄ)]` form) we recover the
