/-- **The single-root principality residual from the sharp class-equality residual.**

Chains `caseIIPrincipalizationAgainstEtaZero_of_anchoredClassTrivial37` with the proven
coprime-generator bridge `exists_not_dvd_spanSingleton_eq_a_div_a_zero_of_etaZeroPrincipalization`
(at the two adjacent roots) to produce `CaseIIAdjacentSingleRootQuotientPrincipal37`. -/
theorem caseIIAdjacentSingleRootQuotientPrincipal37_of_anchoredClassTrivial37
    [NumberField.IsCMField (CyclotomicField 37 ‚Ąö)]
    (h_class : CaseIIAdjacentAnchoredClassTrivial37) :
